title: Lick Library: Learn To Play Randy Rhoads - The Solos
description:
Media: DVD (Region 0) And CD
Language: English
Arrangement: Guitar (GTR)
Artist: Randy Rhoads
Author: Danny Gill

Description

This excellent DVD will show you how to nail five solos by the classical influenced metal Guitar legend! The accompanying CD includes Guitar jam tracks for each solo section at slow, medium and full tempos so you can learn each solo at your own pace and steadily build up to full speed. Solos include; Over The Mountain, Goodbye To Romance, Flying High Again and more!

Songlist

Crazy Train 
Flying High Again 
Goodbye To Romance 
Mr Crowley 
Over The Mountain
